originalSql:
SELECT 
    a.name AS aka_name,
    t.title AS movie_title,
    c.nr_order AS cast_order,
    p.name AS person_name,
    co.name AS company_name,
    k.keyword AS keyword
FROM 
    aka_name a
JOIN 
    cast_info c ON a.person_id = c.person_id
JOIN 
    title t ON c.movie_id = t.id
JOIN 
    name p ON c.person_id = p.imdb_id
JOIN 
    movie_companies mc ON t.id = mc.movie_id
JOIN 
    company_name co ON mc.company_id = co.imdb_id
JOIN 
    movie_keyword mk ON t.id = mk.movie_id
JOIN 
    keyword k ON mk.keyword_id = k.id
WHERE 
    t.production_year > 2000
ORDER BY 
    t.production_year DESC, c.nr_order

SELECT COALESCE("aka_name"."name", "aka_name"."name") AS "AKA_NAME", "title"."title" AS "MOVIE_TITLE", "cast_info"."nr_order" AS "CAST_ORDER", "name"."name" AS "PERSON_NAME", "company_name"."name" AS "COMPANY_NAME", "keyword"."keyword" AS "KEYWORD", "title"."production_year"
FROM "aka_name"
INNER JOIN "cast_info" ON "aka_name"."person_id" = "cast_info"."person_id"
INNER JOIN "title" ON "cast_info"."movie_id" = "title"."id"
INNER JOIN "name" ON "cast_info"."person_id" = "name"."imdb_id"
INNER JOIN "s1" ON "title"."id" = "s1"."movie_id"
INNER JOIN "company_name" ON "s1"."company_id" = "company_name"."imdb_id"
INNER JOIN "movie_keyword" ON "title"."id" = "movie_keyword"."movie_id"
INNER JOIN "keyword" ON "movie_keyword"."keyword_id" = "keyword"."id"
WHERE "title"."production_year" > 2000
ORDER BY "title"."production_year" DESC NULLS FIRST, "cast_info"."nr_order"
